title: Chew(001-042+One-Shots)(2009-Ongoing)(Digital-HD)(Minutemen-Spaz
description:
Chew (001 - 042 + One-Shots) (2009 - Ongoing) (Digital-HD)(Minutemen-Spaztastic+InnerDemons) 


CHEW follows Tony Chu a officer of the law with a unique ability, he is Cibopathic. Which means he gets psychic impressions when he takes a bite out of something living or dead. He has worked with many organizations including the greatest law organization on Earth, The Food and Drug Administration (F.D.A.).

As confirmed by John Layman and Rob Guillory, Chew is a 60 issue comic book.
